# README #

This RESTful with AngularJS application is an implementation of the GroceryList App tutorial found on Udemy.

The restfulapplication and angular-tutorial projects must be deployed onto an Apache Tomcat 7 server.


# RUNNING THE APPLICATION #

Firts of all, we have to make sure to include the MySQL into Tomcat 7 server. To do this, just copy the driver file to the lib folder from Tomcat.

Run the Maven command mvn clean install;
Run the Update Project from Maven menu.